Features :

    1. Toggle Button : to change background and some other css.
    2. Filter : Filter songs on the basis of genre/artist/songs
    3. Search song : type the song and press enter.
    4. play music : click on any of the image or any of the music-button to play.
    5. Next and previous button to move forward and backward.
    6. Add to playlist button used to add that music to current playlist.
    7. create and search playlist 
    8. Only those music in the playlist that are added using "add playlist" can be searched now, but custom playlists can also be searched
    by some simple changes.
    8.Delete Playlist : click on the delete icon.

    That's all about the features and attributes of the Music Player